                    <h1 class="page-header">Secretariat</h1>
                                            <section class="region region-content">
    <div id="block-system-main" class="block block-system">
  <div id="node-5229" class="node node-article clearfix">
  
      <div class="font-bold date"></div>
    
  <div class="summary font-bold"><p>The Secretariat, one of the main organs of the UN, is organized along departmental lines, with each department or office having a distinct area of action and responsibility. Offices and departments coordinate with each other to ensure cohesion as they carry out the day to day work of the Organization in offices and duty stations around the world.&nbsp; At the head of the United Nations Secretariat is the <a href="https://www.un.org/sg/en">Secretary-General</a>.</p>
</div>
  
  <div class="content">
      <div class="field-item teaser-image even"><ul class="links list-inline"><li class="ar first"><a href="http://wss1.un.org/ar/node/8863006/" class="language-link" xml:lang="ar">Ø§ÙØ¹Ø±Ø¨ÙØ©</a></li>
