<div class="field field-name-body field-type-text-with-summary field-label-hidden"><div class="field-items"><div class="field-item even"><h3 class="subhead-light">Secretary-General</h3>
<p>The <a href="https://www.un.org/sg/en/content/role-secretary-general">Secretary-General</a> is the chief administrative officer and head of the Secretariat.</p>
<h3 class="subhead-light">Offices and Departments at Headquarters in New York</h3>
<h5><a href="https://www.un.org/sg/en/global-leadership/executive-office-of-the-secretary-general/all">Executive Office of the Secretary-General</a></h5>
